1.01.name: wordpress/mytwitter
1.01.description: Elitwee allows users to display their recent tweets on their Wordpress site and update their status through the Options page. Includes customization options including number of recent twitters to display, formatting options, and stylesheets. It can be called as a function or used as a widget.
